# Sales Prediction

This project predicts future sales using Machine Learning regression models.
It helps businesses make better decisions based on sales trends and patterns.

## Features
- Data preprocessing and visualization
- Regression-based sales prediction
- Performance evaluation
- Predict future sales values

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib

## Dataset
- Source: Advertising / Sales Dataset
- Features: TV, Radio, Newspaper advertising
- Target: Sales

## Workflow
1. Load and analyze dataset
2. Data preprocessing
3. Feature selection
4. Train regression models
5. Evaluate model performance
6. Predict sales

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository  
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/sales-prediction.git

2. Install dependencies  
   pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Run the script  
   python sales_prediction.py

## Results
- Accurate sales prediction
- Low MAE and RMSE values

## Future Enhancements
- Add deep learning models
- Include more real-world features
- Deploy using Streamlit dashboard

